<Project Sdk="Microsoft.NET.Sdk">

  <!--
    Persistent net10 C# harness project for the Phase-2 REDUCER-REPLAY corpus
    (gen/run-reducer-replay.sh). Replaces the fragile "dafny run, target cs"
    transient path (net8.0, project files auto-generated + deleted per run,
    prone to a stale-net8-artifact class of failures across dafny-version
    upgrades; see git history for the prior spec/replay/*.csproj shape).

    One project, parameterized by the Channel MSBuild property (pass it via
    "-p:Channel=<name>" on the dotnet run command line), is reused across all
    7 channels (root, resourcewatch, changeset, annotations, terminal,
    session, chat): each run of gen/run-reducer-replay.sh first regenerates
    ../build/<Channel>_replay_cs.cs via "dafny translate cs" (with the
    standard-libraries, translate-standard-library, no-verify, and
    include-runtime flags; output set to build/<Channel>_replay_cs) against
    spec/replay/<Channel>_replay.dfy.

    Then this project compiles ONLY that one generated file (see
    EnableDefaultCompileItems=false + the parameterized Compile/Include
    below) and runs it via "dotnet run" against this project, passing
    Channel=<name> plus the fixture paths.

    Switching the Channel property between runs correctly triggers a rebuild
    (MSBuild's up-to-date check sees a different resolved Compile item), even
    when reusing the same shared obj/bin folders; verified empirically
    switching resourcewatch to session and back to resourcewatch with no
    "dotnet clean" between runs.

    No StartupObject is needed: dafny translate's single generated .cs file
    defines exactly one Main (the top-level "class __CallToMain"), unlike
    mapper/Mapper.csproj which co-compiles a hand-written entry point
    alongside the generated file and must disambiguate via StartupObject.

    No PackageReference is needed on net10.0: BigInteger (System.Numerics)
    and ImmutableDictionary (System.Collections.Immutable), which the Dafny
    runtime uses internally, both ship in the shared framework. Per
    gen/CS-HARNESS-PATTERN.md.
  -->
  <PropertyGroup>
    <OutputType>Exe</OutputType>
    <TargetFramework>net10.0</TargetFramework>
    <ImplicitUsings>enable</ImplicitUsings>
    <Nullable>enable</Nullable>
    <EnableDefaultCompileItems>false</EnableDefaultCompileItems>
    <NoWarn>CS8600;CS8603;CS8604;CS8605;CS8625;CS8629;CS8714;CS8765;CS8769;CS8981</NoWarn>
    <RollForward>Major</RollForward>
  </PropertyGroup>

  <ItemGroup>
    <Compile Include="../build/$(Channel)_replay_cs.cs" />
  </ItemGroup>

  <Import Project="../.conflux/runtime/dependencies/conflux-runtime/current/conflux-runtime.props" />

</Project>
